{"tid":1352949,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Telegram救港使用簡介","createTime":"2019-07-23T01:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T02:07:49.000Z","uid":68033,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"836e254130b35505ec2929e2a5ef33b4425cf3fc","tid":1352949,"uid":68033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:02:48.000Z","msg":"自從依幾個月嘅示威起<br />\n唔同嘅Telegram群組不斷發揮作用<br />\n亦有更多人開始使用Telegram<br />\n<br />\n但眼見有唔少手足係基礎設定<br />\n同埋公海Group入面發言都有好多問題<br />\n依類問題如果唔改嘅話<br />\n可能會造成私隱外洩<br />\n同埋溝通效率低下<br />\n所以想講返幾點去改善<br />\n如果大家有補充都可以提出<br />\n<br />\n1.私隱設定<br />\nTelegram最強嘅地方就係私隱度極高<br />\n唔係部電話有後門等等基本上冇事<br />\n但首先都自己做好設定先<br />\n首先去Setting &gt; Privacy and Security <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e0vetKZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe0vetKZ.png&h=aa53f9f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後要Set密碼 熄Touch ID 同埋Set auto lock<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3Xkpi3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3Xkpi3.png&h=a1b9b463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後拉落去Data Settings <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/frk915b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffrk915b.png&h=fd2ac754&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外亦要提到係TG嘅名同大頭相 <br />\n都請唔好用日常用開嘅名/簡稱<br />\n保護自己嘅資料<br />\n<br />\n2.溝通模式<br />\na.近日每當各類行動前<br />\n都會不斷有三毛不斷放流料吹Fake news <br />\n如果大家未經證實就不斷不斷傳<br />\n好容易造成訊息誤傳同恐慌<br />\n近日唔同Group都意識到依個問題做左文宣<br />\n希望大家改善<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DM9hGw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DM9hGw.png&h=3c12b6a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xunkpmy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxunkpmy.png&h=0c221998&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1wEEUT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO1wEEUT.png&h=8316235c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZRk8Oe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZRk8Oe.png&h=800ea364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外都補充下唔同群組都有唔同嘅tag可以用<br />\n例如#未經證實 #現場一手實況 #交通消息 等<br />\n大家用返就可以方便梳理好想要嘅訊息<br />\n<br />\nb.區分語境<br />\n唔同嘅Group有唔同嘅功能<br />\n有D係報料 係D係義載/舉行活動<br />\n建議大家係依類功能性嘅Group<br />\n要管理下自己嘅情緒<br />\n唔好講咁多意氣說話<br />\n明白大家有時會好嬲或者好驚<br />\n但功能群組入面發言愈冷靜愈清楚準確<br />\n溝通嘅效率就愈高愈快<br />\n大家都容易D接受到清晰嘅訊息<br />\n<br />\n大家可以再補充 謝"},{"pid":"56760edf91aa5e19364e619ffbb22a2283dc071b","tid":1352949,"uid":9049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940ef20388f515b42de1c11c9ada930867bcbb69","tid":1352949,"uid":68033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:07:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"258abb72b3a7d9955bcdeb5ff975d7399e4f208f","tid":1352949,"uid":68033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:13:08.000Z","msg":"推一推比其他人睇到"},{"pid":"14092a393b5d133d99ebbf86af301bb427ab5c37","tid":1352949,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:29:33.000Z","msg":"有好多人唔識 幫手推一推"},{"pid":"27d356f85f7b34726ab2452aa272c295995803b6","tid":1352949,"uid":68033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14092a393b5d133d99ebbf86af301bb427ab5c37","tid":1352949,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:29:33.000Z","msg":"有好多人唔識 幫手推一推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"見到好多人用自己名用自己相就衝入黎"},{"pid":"0f5d331a46c4c1e3494490fa5a03fa921b06ca45","tid":1352949,"uid":266733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66bbf8f05b7523ca90ae7715bc19103b9d4dd719","tid":1352949,"uid":68033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a76e8c388109d53251fb10899e